data.description: Beautiful home in the coveted Blackwell Meadows subdivision! 4/2.5 w/ open concept and split floor plan. Granite, LVP, S/S appliances, separate dining opens to galley kitchen. 1/2 bath off of the den. The huge primary suite downstairs has plenty of closet space & double vanities in bath. Upstairs features loft space & 3 add'l bedrooms w/ full bath. Fenced backyard makes this ideal for families
